Property.Name: BodyScript
Property.Value:
BEGIN IF (((SELECT Company.Id FROM Company WHERE Company.Id = @id) IS NULL) OR (@id IS NULL)) BEGIN IF ((SELECT Count(Company.Id) FROM Company WHERE Company.CompanyName = @companyName) = 0) BEGIN INSERT INTO Company(Company.CompanyName) VALUES(@companyName) RETURN @@IDENTITY END
ELSE BEGIN RETURN -1 END END
ELSE BEGIN IF ((SELECT Count(Company.Id) FROM Company WHERE Company.CompanyName = @companyName) = 0) BEGIN UPDATE Company SET Company.CompanyName = @companyName, Company.CreationTime = GetDate() WHERE Company.Id = @id RETURN @id END
ELSE BEGIN RETURN -2 END END END
